faq_delivery_answer_3: Yes, we deliver on Saturdays from 10:00 to 18:00. Sunday deliveries are available for urgent orders with an additional fee. Please contact our support to arrange weekend delivery.
faq_delivery_question_4: What payment methods do you accept?
faq_delivery_answer_4: We accept cash on delivery, bank cards (Visa, MasterCard, Elcard), bank transfers, and mobile payment systems (Mbank, O! Money, MegaPay). Online payments through our website are also available.
faq_delivery_answer_5: Yes, after placing your order, you will receive a tracking number via SMS and email. You can track your order status in real-time through our website or mobile app.
faq_delivery_question_6: Do you deliver to other cities?
faq_delivery_answer_6: Yes, we deliver to all major cities in Kyrgyzstan including Osh, Jalal-Abad, Karakol, Naryn, Talas, and Batken. Delivery times vary by location.
faq_delivery_question_7: What if I'm not home during delivery?
faq_delivery_answer_7: Our courier will contact you before arrival. If you're unavailable, we can reschedule delivery for another time or you can pick up your order from our warehouse.
faq_delivery_answer_8: Currently, we only deliver within Kyrgyzstan. For international orders, please contact our support for custom arrangements.
faq_returns_question_2: How do I return a product?
faq_returns_answer_2: Contact our support to initiate a return. We will arrange a courier pickup or provide a return address. Returns are free for defective products.
faq_returns_question_3: How long does refund processing take?
faq_returns_answer_3: Refunds are processed within 3-5 business days after we receive the returned product. The time it takes for the refund to appear in your account depends on your payment method.
faq_returns_answer_4: We provide a 1-year warranty on all motorcycle equipment from the date of purchase. The warranty covers manufacturing defects but not damage from improper use or accidents.
faq_returns_question_5: Can I exchange a product instead of returning it?
faq_returns_answer_5: Yes, you can exchange products within 14 days for a different size, color, or model. Exchanges are subject to product availability.
faq_products_answer_2: Yes, all our products are 100% original with official warranties. We are authorized dealers for major brands like AGV, HJC, Shark, Alpinestars, and others.
faq_products_question_3: How do I care for motorcycle gear?
faq_products_answer_3: Leather gear requires special leather cleaner and conditioner. Textile gear can be washed with mild detergent. Helmets should be cleaned with mild soap and water only - never use chemicals.
faq_products_answer_4: Yes, our physical store has fitting rooms where you can try on helmets, jackets, pants, and boots. We recommend visiting for proper fitting of safety equipment.
faq_products_question_5: Can I order products not listed on your website?
faq_products_answer_5: Yes, we can special order many products not listed on our website. Contact our support with product details, and we'll check availability and pricing.
faq_products_question_6: What certifications do your helmets have?
faq_products_answer_6: Our helmets meet ECE 22.06, DOT, or both certifications depending on the model. These are international safety standards for motorcycle helmets.
faq_service_answer_2: Yes, we repair leather gear, textile jackets, and some types of gloves. We also replace helmet visors and interior padding. Contact us for a repair estimate.
faq_service_question_3: How often should I replace my helmet?
faq_service_answer_3: Replace your helmet every 5 years or immediately after any significant impact, even if no damage is visible. The protective materials degrade over time.
faq_service_answer_4: Yes, we offer maintenance services for motorcycle gear including cleaning, conditioning, zipper repair, and waterproofing re-treatment for textile gear.
faq_other_question_2: Can I get a corporate discount?
faq_other_answer_2: Yes, we offer corporate discounts for bulk purchases, motorcycle clubs, and riding schools. Contact our business sales department for more information.
